........... Update frequency and content standards
........... Escalation communication failures
1.1.6 Incident Closure & Validation
........... Closure codes and resolution evidence
........... Customer confirmation vs auto-closure risks
........... Post-incident review triggers
1.2 Problem Management (Root Cause, Known Errors)
1.2.1 Incident vs Problem Distinction
........... Symptom suppression vs root cause elimination
........... Risks of overusing incidents
1.2.2 Reactive vs Proactive Problem Management
........... Trend-based problem identification
........... Major incident follow-up as problem input
1.2.3 Root Cause Analysis (RCA)
........... Techniques (5 Whys, Fishbone, Fault Tree)
........... Root cause vs contributing factors
1.2.4 Known Error Records (KERs)
........... Purpose and lifecycle
........... Workaround documentation standards
........... Operational value of known errors
1.2.5 Problem Closure & Prevention
........... Validation of permanent fixes
........... Measuring problem management effectiveness

