1.5.5 CMDB Governance
Data ownership
Validation and reconciliation

1.6 Section Exit Criteria (Pass / Fail)
You pass Section 1 only if:
You can predict SLA behavior without tools
You prevent misclassification before it hits ops
You challenge risky changes confidently
You treat CMDB as a risk tool, not a diagram
Fail here → you are not operationally safe.

